ereignty, adherence to international law, and balancing security with economic cooperation, comes ahead of US President Donald Trump's visit to China amid ongoing regional tensions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-envoy-backs-xi-jinpings-four-point-gulf-security-plan-ahead-of-trumps-china-visit/articleshow/131036029.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-envoy-backs-xi-jinpings-four-point-gulf-security-plan-ahead-of-trumps-china-visit/articleshow/131036029.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T16:11:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131036101,imgsize-570966.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kuwait launches new Sahel Service for flight delays, refunds and lost baggage complaints]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131036512.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kuwait's aviation regulator has launched a new feature on the Sahel app, allowing air travelers to directly report flight delays, cancellations, and refund disputes. This digital service aims to expedite complaint handling and enhance passenger protection, simplifying communication between passengers, airlines, and authorities.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/kuwait-launches-new-sahel-service-for-flight-delays-refunds-and-lost-baggage-complaints/articleshow/131036512.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/kuwait-launches-new-sahel-service-for-flight-delays-refunds-and-lost-baggage-complaints/articleshow/131036512.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T16:08:36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url